            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab>(C.) In nomine sanctae et individuae trinitatis. <persName
                            key="#Emperor/king" ref="#people/130">Heinricus</persName> divina
                        favente clementia <rs key="#Emperor/king">rex</rs>. Si sanctis ac
                        venerabilibus locis eo, quae ab antecessoribus nostris collata sunt,
                        corroborare studuerimus et de his, que nostri iuris sunt, concedere
                        satagimus, aeterne vite emolumentum adipisci ac presentis status soliditatem
                        propensius augmentari non titubamus. Idcirco omnium fidelium sanctae dei
                        aecclesiae nostrorumque presentium ac futurorum industria noverit, Vv. <rs
                            key="#Abbots">abbatem</rs> et <rs key="#Monks">monachos</rs> in <rs
                            key="#Monasteries">coenobio</rs>
                        <orgName
                            key="#Burgi #Houses #Curtes #Casae/cassinae_massaricie #Landed_possessions #Wine #Decima #Public_exactions #Churches #Monasteries #Cells/hermitages #Abbots #Monks #Royal_slave"
                            ref="#juridical_persons/301">domini et salvatoris nostri Iesu
                            Christi</orgName> militantes in <placeName ref="#places/737">monte
                            Amate</placeName> nobis lacrimabiliter protulisse, quod famis ac
                        nuditatis indigentia ibidem deo servire non possent, eo quod <rs
                            key="#Curtes">cortes</rs> et <rs key="#Cells/hermitages">celle</rs>,
                        quae a precessoribus ad sumptum eorum conlate sunt, a pravis fuissent
                        distracte hominibus. Nos quidem pro dei amore animarumque nostrarum remedio,
                        quoniam idem coenobium in nostram devenerat potestatem ac proprietatem, res
                        et predia, quae a nostris precessoribus collata sunt et confirmata ac
                        corroborata, confirmare et corroborare studuimus et <rs
                            key="#Fiscal_property #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches">de nostris iuris
                            proprietate in monachorum sumptum</rs> cortes et cellas contulimus,
                        quatinus sedulo orationes pro nobis <rs key="#legallyRecognisedUnionWith"
                            >coniugeque</rs> nostra <persName
                            key="#Queen #legallyRecognisedUnionWith" ref="#people/131"
                            >Cunigunda</persName>
                        <rs key="#Queen">regina</rs> ibidem ad dominum dirigatur. Igitur cortes et
                        cellas, <rs key="#Casae/cassinae_massaricie">massaricia</rs> et <rs
                            key="#Landed_possessions">sortes</rs>
                        <rs key="#Royal_slave">familiamque utriusque sexus</rs>, quae actenus
                        tenuerunt, omniaque precepta ab antecessoribus nostris conlata omniaque
                        instrumenta confirmamus pleniterque corroboramus, et quoniam prefatum
                        coenobium in nostram devenit potestatem et proprietatem, et quae a pravis
                        ablata sunt hominibus et alia, quibus indigentia explere valeant, in usum
                        fratrum per hoc nostrum preceptum concedimus donamus atque largimus,
                        videlicet <geogName
                            key="#Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches"
                            ref="#estates/2312">Rotam cardosam, quae nunc Burgoricho
                            nuncupatur</geogName>, et medietatem curte <geogName
                            key="#Curtes #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches"
                            ref="#estates/2313">sancti Sebastiani</geogName> et <rs key="#Burgi"
                            >burgo</rs> de <placeName key="#Burgi">Uultiole</placeName> et <rs
                            key="#Curtes">curte</rs> de <geogName
                            key="#Curtes #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches"
                            ref="#estates/2314">Climintiano</geogName> et <rs key="#Castle"
                            >Rocka</rs> de <placeName key="#Castle" ref="#places/2733"
                            >Senzano</placeName> cum suis pertinentiis, <rs key="#Curtes">curte</rs>
                        de <geogName
                            key="#Curtes #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches"
                            ref="#estates/2315">Fereniano</geogName>, curte in <geogName
                            key="#Curtes" ref="#estates/2316">Corsiniano</geogName>, <rs
                            key="#Houses">casis</rs> et <rs key="#Landed_possessions">terris
                            domnicatis</rs> in <placeName key="#Houses #Landed_possessions"
                            >Cingona</placeName> et iuxta <rs key="#Rivers">flumen qui vocatur
                            Urcea</rs>, et curte in <geogName
                            key="#Curtes #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches"
                            ref="#estates/335">Titinano</geogName>, curte et cella <orgName
                            key="#Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches #Cells/hermitages"
                            ref="#juridical_persons/302">sanctae Mariae qui vocatur Lamule</orgName>
                        cum suis pertinentiis, curte in <geogName
                            key="#Curtes #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches"
                            ref="#estates/2317">Campagnatico</geogName>, <rs key="#Cells/hermitages"
                            >cella</rs> et <rs key="#Curtes">curte</rs> in <placeName
                            key="#Curtes #Cells/hermitages">Garmarita</placeName> cum suis <rs
                            key="#Wine">vineis</rs> qui vocatur <placeName key="#Wine"
                            ref="#places/2735">Poppae in Cornito</placeName>, <rs key="#Curtes"
                            >curte</rs>
                        <orgName
                            key="#Curtes #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches"
                            >sanctae Mariae in Ualeriano</orgName> cum ipsis rebus de Cortitiano cum
                        omnibus adiacentiis et pertinentiis earum, <rs key="#Cells/hermitages"
                            >cella</rs>
                        <orgName
                            key="#Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches #Cells/hermitages"
                            >sancti Sauini</orgName> nec non et <orgName
                            key="#Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches #Cells/hermitages"
                            >sancti Stephani</orgName> et <orgName
                            key="#Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches #Cells/hermitages"
                            ref="#juridical_persons/1452">sanctae Restitutae in <placeName
                                ref="#places/430">Terquino</placeName></orgName>, seu etiam curte
                            <geogName
                            key="#Curtes #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches"
                            ref="#estates/2334">sancti Seueri</geogName> super <rs key="#Lakes"
                            >lacum</rs> cum ipsa <rs key="#Curtes">corticella</rs> de <geogName
                            key="#Curtes #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches"
                            ref="#estates/333">Bisentio</geogName>, cellam etiam <orgName
                            key="#Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_churches #Cells/hermitages"
                            >sancti Miniati</orgName> nec non et cellam <orgName
                            key="#Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches #Cells/hermitages"
                            ref="#juridical_persons/308">sancti Salvatoris in <placeName
                                ref="#places/762">valle Racana</placeName></orgName>, curte
                            <geogName
                            key="#Curtes #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches"
                            ref="#estates/2311">sancti Petri in Ceruaria</geogName> cum <rs
                            key="#Curtes">corticella</rs> in <placeName key="#Curtes"
                            >Capago</placeName> cum omnibus rebus et familiis ad eas in integrum
                        pertinentibus vel respicientibus. Denique etiam concedimus ad predictum
                        coenobium omnia <rs key="#Decima">decima</rs> frea et iudiciaria et omnem
                        compositionem et <rs key="#Public_exactions">exibitionem</rs> pu[b]licam ex
                        omnibus manentibus predicti monasterii ob remedium a[ni]marum nostrarum in
                        usum peregrinorum ad portam monasterii clamantium. Precepimus etiam et
                        statuimus, ut deinceps in futurum haec nostra confirmatio atque donatio a
                        posteris nostris inconvulsa maneat et inlibata, et ut nullus dux marchio
                        comes vicecomes aut ulla regni nostri magna parvaque persona in domos vel
                        res predicti monasterii violentiam inferat aut famulos flagellare vel
                        angariare presumat neque de predictis rebus ullam minorationem facere
                        satagat, sed liceat abbatem sanctamque congregationem predictas cortes et
                        cellas cum eorum integritatibus tenere, omnium inquietudine remota. Si quis
                        hoc nostrum preceptum violare temptaverit, se compositurum <rs
                            key="#Penalty">auri optimi libras centum</rs>, <rs key="#Camera_regis"
                            >medietatem kamere nostrae</rs> et <rs
                            key="#Camera_of_other_public_authorities">medietatem sanctae
                            congregationi predicti coenobii</rs>. Quod ut verius credatur et
                        diligentius observetur, manibus propriis corroborantes anuli nostri
                        inpressione subter iussimus insigniri. Signum domni Heinrici (M.) regis
                        invictissimi. Â  <persName key="#Chancellor"><name ref="Everardus"
                                >Eberhardus</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Chancellor">cancellarius</rs> vice <persName><name ref="Uillegis"
                                >Uuilligisi</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Archchaplain">archicapellani</rs> recognovi. Data IIII. idus
                        april. indictione IIII, anno dominicae incarnationis MVI, anno vero domni
                        Heinrici secundi regnantis V; actum <placeName ref="#places/2736"
                            >Radesbonae</placeName>. (B. D.)</ab>
                </div>
